WEBVTT

00:06.963 --> 00:08.367
ï»¿Take a look at these eyes.

00:08.945 --> 00:12.232
Right now you're probably starting to feel rather self-conscious.

00:12.834 --> 00:16.059
Perhaps more surprisingly, research shows that because of that,...

00:16.263 --> 00:18.627
...you're more likely to behave in an honest way...

00:18.895 --> 00:20.920
...and show greater levels of self-control.

00:21.617 --> 00:24.381
In fact, work from the University of Newcastle shows...

00:24.463 --> 00:27.598
...that simply placing a poster of eyes near a bicycle rack...

00:27.834 --> 00:31.004
...reduces theft by a remarkable 65 percent.

00:31.555 --> 00:33.829
And the same effect can help you lose weight.

00:34.399 --> 00:38.641
Psychologist Brad Bushman has discovered that when people see themselves in a mirror,...

00:38.794 --> 00:41.935
...they become more self-conscious and so eat more healthily.

